import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.minimum(x1, x0)
    v1 = jnp.sin(x0)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(x0, x0)
    v3 = jnp.subtract(v2, v1)
    v4 = jnp.subtract(v3, v3)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(x0, v4)
    v6 = jnp.abs(v2)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(x0, v5)
    v8 = jnp.maximum(v5, v0)
    return v8
